      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a heavy burden, but remember that you are no longer just a ghost; you are the person who has to rebuild, even if the walls are different now. Surviving another day doesn't mean you have to fix everything immediately, it just means you get through the morning before the exhaustion takes over completely. You are stronger than you feel in this moment, and that strength will be enough to keep you safe until you can find your way back to yourself.",
