      "content": "i don't want to \"find my way back.\" there is nothing left to find. it's not even about being strong anymore, it's just... the pain is so constant. it's like a physical weight on my chest. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not feel anything anymore. is it even wrong to want that? to just want the hurting to end for good?",
